Prerequisites : StoreFront application database in MySQL (done in DBMS sessions/assignments) 


Assignment 1:***************************************
Given the id of a user, fetch all orders (Id, Order Date, Order Total) of that user which are in shipped state. 
Orders should be sorted by order date column in chronological order.

Assignment 2:***************************************
Insert five or more images of a product using batch insert technique.

Assignment 3:***************************************
set  all those products which were not ordered by any Shopper in last 1 year as inactive and return number of inactive products.

Assignment 4:***************************************
Select and display the category title of all top parent categories sorted alphabetically 
and the count of their child categories.



Note:
All the database queries should be at one place. 
Result should be wrapped in POJOs.
Proper Exception handling.
Good to create helper class for querying the database and wrapping the results.